"title": "8339: self-control",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8339",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Physical and emotional self-mastery, particularly in situations of intense provocation or temptation.</p>\n<h2>Self-control is the mark of a wise person</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:11\">PRO 29:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:1-Prov1:5\">PRO 1:1–1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Self-control is an aspect of Christian character</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:12\">TIT 2:11–2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2\">1TI 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:8\">TIT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:2\">TIT 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:5-Titus2:6\">TIT 2:5–2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:9\">2PE 1:5–1:9</a></p>\n<h2>Self-control affects the whole person</h2>\n<h3>Physical self-control</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:26-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:26–9:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:36-1Cor7:38\">1CO 7:36–7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:3–4:7</a></p>\n<h3>A mental discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:13\">1PE 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:6-1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:6–5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:7\">1PE 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a></p>\n<h3>Controlled speech</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:3\">PSA 141:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:19\">JAS 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:3\">PSA 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:23\">PRO 16:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:23\">PRO 21:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:2\">ECC 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1-Jas3:12\">JAS 3:1–3:12</a></p>\n<h2>Self-control in response to persecution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:39-Matt5:40\">MAT 5:39–5:40</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27-Luke6:29\">LUK 6:27–6:29</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:18-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:18–2:23</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of self-control</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:7-Gen39:12\">GEN 39:7–39:12</a> <em>Joseph</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:1-1Sam24:7\">1SA 24:1–24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:7-1Sam26:12\">1SA 26:7–26:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:9-2Sam16:10\">2SA 16:9–16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:1\">JOB 31:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:30\">JOB 31:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7\">ISA 53:7</a> <em>the servant, understood in the NT as a prophecy concerning Jesus Christ</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:61\">MRK 14:61</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:27-Matt27:30\">MAT 27:27–27:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:12-1Cor4:13\">1CO 4:12–4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:24–9:27</a></p>\n<h2>The dangers of a loss of self-control</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:7\">PRO 18:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:10\">JER 14:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10-1Sam18:11\">1SA 18:10–18:11</a> <em>Saul</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:7-2Sam13:14\">2SA 13:7–13:14</a> <em>Amnon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:32-Ps106:33\">PSA 106:32–106:33</a> <em>Moses</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:1-Prov6:3\">PRO 6:1–6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:18\">PRO 29:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:25\">ACT 24:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24-Rom1:31\">ROM 1:24–1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:5\">1CO 7:5</a> <em>aimed at those who thought that abstaining from sexual relations in marriage was spiritual</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:9\">1CO 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:232\">COL 2:232</a>PE <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:12-Col2:14\">2:12–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18-2Pet2:19\">2PE 2:18–2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:4\">JUD 1:4</a></p>",
